WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:02.500
Anna has helped organise an excursion.

00:02.700 --> 00:08.100
Part of her tent village wants to hike
 to the lake ten kilometres away to swim.

00:08.200 --> 00:11.100
Beforehand, they all have to assure her 
 that they can swim.

00:11.150 --> 00:14.900
Amid loud singing and much joy,
 twenty children set off.
